UnitLPUSD::constructor
├── when deployed with zero vaultManager address
│   └── it reverts
└── when deployed with valid vaultManager address
    ├── it sets VAULT_MANAGER
    ├── it sets the token name
    └── it sets the token symbol


UnitLPUSD::mint
├── when called by a non-vaultManager
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by the vaultManager
    └── it mints tokens to the recipient


UnitLPUSD::burn
├── when called by a non-vaultManager
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by the vaultManager
    └── it burns tokens from the account
